    <body>
        <p>By default, <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" />'s dynamic Help is now hosted online, rather than inside the application. This allows topics to be updated on an as-needed basis with the most current information. In previous versions of <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" />, the dynamic Help was only updated when there was a new product release. </p>
        <p>To open the dynamic Help for the active element in the interface, select <span class="Emphasis">Help&gt;Dynamic Help</span>. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Interface/UI_Elements/Dynamic_Help_Window.htm">Dynamic Help Window Pane</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
        <p MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">
            <img src="../../../../Images/dynamic_help1.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <p MadCap:conditions="Products.Lingo">
            <img src="../../../../Images/dynamic_help1_lingo.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth85Percent" />
        </p>
        <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="FlareGuides.FlareWhatsNewGuide" />
        <p>You can also open the full online Help in your browser. To do this, you can click the <span class="Emphasis">Open Topic in Browser</span> button at the top of the dynamic Help window pane.</p>
        <p MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">
            <img src="../../../../Images/dynamic_help2.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <p MadCap:conditions="Products.Lingo">
            <img src="../../../../Images/dynamic_help2_lingo.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <MadCap:pageBreak MadCap:conditions="FlareGuides.FlareWhatsNewGuide,LingoGuides.LingoWhatsNewGuide" />
        <p>You can also select <span class="Emphasis">Help&gt;Open Help</span>.</p>
        <p MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">
            <img src="../../../../Images/open_help.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <p MadCap:conditions="Products.Lingo">
            <img src="../../../../Images/open_help_lingo.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
    </body>
</html>